data.description: Beautiful 3/2.5 home in a mature, desirable neighborhood. minutes from Lenoir City schools, 15 minutes from west Knoxville/Turkey Creek and 30 minutes from Downtown Knoxville and the airport. This immaculately updated home offers so many improvements! On the exterior, owners have recently installed new roof,6'   gutters, new garage door w/ coated floor, storm door, Trex deck, refurbished railing, exterior lighting updates, and a privacy fence all on a cleared, spacious corner lot with a mountain view. Inside, owners have updated with new paint, new laminate flooring downstairs, new carpet upstairs, new granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, beautiful new bathroom tile, and stainless appliances that stay. Owners updated every light fixture throughout. New faucets, sinks w/ garbage disposal, toilets, and much more. Primary bedroom is on the main floor, and all rooms have generous walk-in closets. The house is ready for you to come love it for years and years to come.
